Author: Gateway#3763
Content:
[telegram] <sreinhardt> Hey there Steve, 
Well, this wouldnt really be a new exchange listing, it's a popular blockchain metric site that shows how much use chains really get. It's easy to hype your chain, but if nobody is using it then what's the point? This side shows how much a given chain is actually used. Komodo is doing really well on it but is being hampered because of the parallel design of the Komodo ecosystem. I'm talking about seeing if the metric reporting site would show Komodo in a more accurate light, taking all the sidechains to Komodo into account, which would make us look even more impressive against other chains out there. (re @guildleader: listing would be really cool. New exchange more opportunities.)
